				<wikidot:authorName>XCninety</wikidot:authorName>				<wikidot:authorUserId>3713295</wikidot:authorUserId>				<content:encoded>
					<![CDATA[
						 <p>There is a sentence in the containment procedure saying</p> <blockquote> <p>If <span style="text-decoration: underline;">SCP-1091-1</span> transfers to another radio transmitting device, all personnel are instructed to seek out and destroy all radio devices within a 5&#160;km radius:</p> </blockquote> <p>which actually should be &quot;SCP-1091&quot; in my opinion. Is this a typo?</p> 
				 	]]>
				</content:encoded>							</item>
					<item>
