						 <p>Image is <a href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/kb8wfh/230174386/in/pool-63222078@N00/">not compliant with CC 3.0</a>. As such, it has since been removed.</p> <p>Second image could not be sourced to anywhere except <a href="https://www.wattpad.com/1101713-so-nearly-free">here</a>, and is assumed not compliant for being unable to be sourced reliably. It is pending removal/replacement.</p> <p>Belated update: image has been replaced, provided by <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/edna-granbo" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=2212713&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1583977982" alt="Edna Granbo" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=2212713)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/edna-granbo" >Edna Granbo</a></span>. It is compliant with CC BY-SA 3.0.</p> <p>Original image is derived from <a href="https://commons.wikimedia.org/wiki/File:Extended_arm.jpg">here</a>, which is licensed under CC 4.0.</p> 
				 	]]>
