					<![CDATA[
						 <p>Read upthread. This wasn't meant to be referencing Russian Sleep Experiment.</p> <p>I don't like Russian Sleep Experiment (it's narmy as all Hell if you ask me), and I don't like this either, but for other reasons.</p> <p>I am pretty sure that audio clip really is that picture turned into an SSTV signal, and even though the person reading (presumably the author) was not fantastic, turning a picture into an SSTV signal is above and beyond what's normally expected, so I have to commend that.</p> <p>However, I wasn't entertained and have voted accordingly.</p> 
				 	]]>
				</content:encoded>							</item>
